# CSS Animations

Animations allow elements to move and change automatically.

## Keyframes

```css
@keyframes slide {
    from {
        transform: translateX(0);
    }

    to {
        transform: translateX(200px);
    }
}
```

## Apply Animation

```css
.box {
    animation: slide 2s infinite;
}
```

## Animation Properties

- animation-name
- animation-duration
- animation-delay
- animation-iteration-count

## Real-World Example

Loading spinners use animations.

## Benefits

- Attractive UI
- Improved engagement
- Better user feedback

## Summary

Animations make websites more interactive.
